source:
TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_SEQ_00<tab>By the look in her eyes, Qhoterl Pasol has tools on her mind.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>Règle spéciale<var 1D /var>:  synchronisation de quête avec limitation de job ou de classe<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
<var 1A 02 /var>* Il n'est possible de progresser dans cette quête qu'avec la classe qui a servi à la commencer.<var 1A 01 /var>

Qhoterl Pasol a besoin de matériaux pour fabriquer des outils d'excavation.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_SEQ_01<tab>Deliver the requested items to Qhoterl Pasol.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_SEQ_01<tab>Livrer ce qui vous a été demandé à Qhoterl Pasol

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E4E80511 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Mine splendid iron ore in the Blind Forest of Yx'Maja)) ((Deliver the splendid iron ore to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80512 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Gather splendid flax in the Blind Forest of Yx'Maja)) ((Deliver the splendid flax to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80513 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Catch a splendid clawbow at Mjrl's Regret)) ((Deliver the splendid clawbow to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) (()) /var>)) /var>)) /var>.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E4E80511 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Extraire <var 33 ((Item)) 02E8060302 /var> dans la forêt interdite d'Yx'Maja)) ((Livrer <var 33 ((Item)) 03E8060302 /var> à Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80512 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Récolter <var 33 ((Item)) 02E8060302 /var> dans la forêt interdite d'Yx'Maja)) ((Livrer <var 33 ((Item)) 03E8060302 /var> à Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80513 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Pêcher <var 33 ((Item)) 02E8060202 /var> en aval de la Nostalgie de Mjrl)) ((Livrer <var 33 ((Item)) 03E8060202 /var> à Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) (()) /var>)) /var>)) /var>

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Rigorously as we work, we quickly wear down our tools until there's nothing left save the hilt. And a tool with only a hilt is no tool at all, I'm sure you'll agree.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Qhoterl Pasol avoir besoin de beaucouuup d'outils<var 1D /var>! Outils s'uuuser très vite, alors toujours besoin de nouveaux<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>To be sure, not <var 1A 02 /var>all<var 1A 01 /var> of our implements have hilts, but the point stands that we need to replace them quite regularly. And it's my responsibility to ensure that we always have the materials with which to make them.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>Pour fabriquer ouuutils, beaucoup matériaux in<var 16 /var>dis<var 16 /var>pen<var 16 /var>sa<var 16 /var>bles<var 1D /var>! <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> aider Qhoterl Pasol a récupérer matériaux, d'accord<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_010<tab>To that end, I'd be much obliged if you could mine for me, shall we say, three chunks of iron ore. They can be found in the Blind Forest of Yx'Maja. My thanks in advance, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_010<tab>Toi aller dans forêt d'Yx'Maja et extraire trois <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF2734D0302 /var><var 1D /var>! Comme ça, Qhoterl Pasol contente contente<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_020<tab>To that end, I'd be much obliged if you could gather for me, shall we say, three clumps of flax. They can be found in the Blind Forest of Yx'Maja. My thanks in advance, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_020<tab>Toi aller dans forêt d'Yx'Maja et récolter trois <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF273670302 /var><var 1D /var>! Comme ça, Qhoterl Pasol contente contente<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030<tab>To that end, I'd be much obliged if you could catch a clawbow for me. They're native to the Blind Forest of Yx'Maja, and I'm given to understand that fruit worms make the best bait. My thanks in advance, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030<tab>Toi aller en aval de la Nostalgie de Mjrl et pêcher <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF273810202 /var> avec <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF26BBE0202 /var><var 1D /var>! Comme ça, Qhoterl Pasol contente contente<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_100_010<tab>Remember, it's three chunks of iron ore I require. You will find them in the Blind Forest of Yx'Maja. My thanks in advance, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_100_010<tab>Toi aller dans forêt d'Yx'Maja et extraire trois <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF2734D0302 /var><var 1D /var>! Comme ça, Qhoterl Pasol contente contente<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_100_020<tab>Remember, it's three clumps of flax I require. You will find them in the Blind Forest of Yx'Maja. My thanks in advance, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_100_020<tab>Toi aller dans forêt d'Yx'Maja et récolter trois <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF273670302 /var><var 1D /var>! Comme ça, Qhoterl Pasol contente contente<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_100_030<tab>Remember, it's a clawbow I require. They're native to the Blind Forest of Yx'Maja, and I'm given to understand that fruit worms make the best bait. My thanks in advance, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_100_030<tab>Toi aller en aval de la Nostalgie de Mjrl et pêcher <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF273810202 /var> avec <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF26BBE0202 /var><var 1D /var>! Comme ça, Qhoterl Pasol contente contente<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_050<tab>Jolly good, you're returned. And with the requested item, I trust?
TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_060<tab>My, such splendid chunks of ore these are! They shall make the sturdiest shovels and pickaxes, oh yes!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_060<tab>Oooh, comme c'est beauuu<var 1D /var>! Avec ça, Qhoterl Pasol fabriquer pelles et pioches bien solides<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_070<tab>My, such splendid clumps of flax these are! They shall make the sturdiest rope, oh yes!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_070<tab>Oooh, comme c'est beauuu<var 1D /var>! Avec ça, Qhoterl Pasol fabriquer cordes bien solides<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_080<tab>My, such a splendid specimen of clawbow this is! Their sturdy pincers can find use in many a tool, oh yes. My gratitude, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_080<tab>Oooh, comme c'est beauuu<var 1D /var>! Avec grosses pinces, Qhoterl Pasol fabriquer plein d'ouuutils très résistants<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_090<tab>Thanks to your kind assistance, we have all that we require for now, but we'll have need of more before long. I hope that you'll lend us your procuring expertise again.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ101_03806_QHOTERLPASOL_000_090<tab>Merci beauuucoup, merci beauuuucoup<var 1D /var>! Nous toujours avoir besoin matériaux, alors toi revenir aider quand toi vouloir<var 1D /var>!
